snippet.title: The Pocket Master - Use your magical pocket to change objects size and please everyone!
snippet.description:
Download for free on itch.io https://antoine-foucault.itch.io/the-pocket-master?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt As the Pocket Master, you job is to help people in need.

Use your magical pocket to change objects size and please everyone!

Pocket everything! Objects, people, entire rooms... The pocket world has no limit.
